title: Brie's pumpkinlicious dog treat bites
ingredients: ['190g wholemeal flour (DO NOT use plain white flour)', '120g cooked and mashed pumpkin', '80g rolled oats', '4 tablespoons natural smooth peanut butter', '4 tablespoons water', '2 tablespoons rapeseed oil', '2 teaspoons baking powder', '1 teaspoon allspice']
